        },
        "committer": {
          "name": "Alexander.Boyko",
          "email": "alexander_boyko@xyratex.com",
          "date": "2012-03-28 12:57:45.000000000",
          "tz": 240
        },
        "subject": "LU-1247 obdfilter: fix invalid check of precrate objects",
        "message": "LU-1247 obdfilter: fix invalid check of precrate objects\n\nMDT precreate objects when it has objects count less than the\noscc->oscc_grow_count / 2. oscc->oscc_grow_count can be equal\nto OST_MAX_PRECREATE, so MDT (last_id - next_id) is less than the\n(OST_MAX_PRECREAT * 3 / 2). This patch fix the wrong condition at\nfilter_handle_precreate() when delete orphans request happend.\n\nSigned-off-by: Alexander Boyko <alexander_boyko@xyratex.com>\nReviewed-by: Andrew Perepechko <andrew_perepechko@xyratex.com>\nReviewed-by: Andriy Skulysh <andriy_skulysh@xyratex.com>\nXyratex-bug-id: MRP-440\nChange-Id: I5bac3ee7261fe7462254bd80565d770041c3c206\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
